de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.gatt

Interface PulseOximeterGattLibrary

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GattLibrary
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BLE113lib

    public interface PulseOximeterGattLibrary
extends GattLibrary
    This interface defines two methods which will return the required handles to enable pulse oximeter notifications and data interpretation. The API may be expanded in the future for additional data.
    Author:
    Daniel Pyka

    • Method Detail

      • getHandlePulseOximeterMeasurement

        String getHandlePulseOximeterMeasurement()
        Retrieve the handle address of the sensor for pulse oximeter data. This address can be checked if the incoming notification really is a pulse oximeter notification.
        Returns:
        handle address of pulse oximeter data

      • getHandlePulseOximeterNotification

        String getHandlePulseOximeterNotification()
        Retrieve the handle address which is used to enable/ disable pulse oximeter notifications.
        Returns:
        handle address to enable/ disable pulse oximeter notifications
